      "content": "\"Do not mistake this imposition for mere conquest; it is a profound act of salvation. We are not crushing them, we are elevating them from the mire of their own savage inclinations. Their traditions, while colorful, are ultimately shackles preventing their ascent to true humanity. By introducing our laws and our ways, we are offering them the only true path to dignity—a path that only the enlightened can provide.\"",
